# Cloudflare Pages headers
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
#
# Security headers only. NOTE: a Cache-Control override was tried here
# and verified NOT to work for static assets - Pages applies custom
# security headers to assets but ignores Cache-Control overrides on
# them (they keep Pages' own 4-hour asset cache; HTML is always
# max-age=0). Cache-busting is handled with ?v= query strings on the
# asset links in each HTML file instead - bump those on changes.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
